Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽並沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.34,0:00:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使放了煙花 小芽也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
